## Firestore Schema

### Collection: `agent_commands/{commandId}`

| Field         | Type                                                              | Description                                    |
|---------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------|
| `userId`      | `string`                                                          | Scopes the command to the authenticated user   |
| `instruction` | `string`                                                          | The task/prompt dispatched to OpenClaw         |
| `status`      | `'pending' \| 'running' \| 'complete' \| 'error' \| 'cancelled'` | Lifecycle state                                |
| `model`       | `string?`                                                         | Optional: `'gemini-2.5'`, `'gpt-4o'`, etc.    |
| `agentLabel`  | `string?`                                                         | Human-readable label, e.g. `"Scan Project Akh"` |
| `createdAt`   | `Timestamp`                                                       | Written by the UI on dispatch                  |
| `result`      | `string?`                                                         | Written back by OpenClaw on completion         |
| `completedAt` | `Timestamp?`                                                      | Written back by OpenClaw on completion         |

